{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/summary-2020-plans-for-2021/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"marcingladkowski.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3b607386-b659-5272-8fa3-ffa04fb840cb","excerpt":"This year - i mean 2020 was an unusual year for everyone - I think.\nTherefore each should summarize own actions. In this post I will write what i have achieved in 2020\nand what i want to achieve in 2…","html":"<p>This year - i mean 2020 was an unusual year for everyone - I think.\nTherefore each should summarize own actions. In this post I will write what i have achieved in 2020\nand what i want to achieve in 2021.</p>\n<p>In last few days I created this blog. It's another shoot to still practicing writing blog posts.</p>\n<p>How looks this year on github ? Not bad, not good.\n<figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/d43c10d4a849544d46f32e40d143b2f8/e4da8/github.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 24.705882352941178%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='image-center' title='' src='/static/d43c10d4a849544d46f32e40d143b2f8/ca1dc/github.png' srcset='/static/d43c10d4a849544d46f32e40d143b2f8/e7570/github.png 170w,\n/static/d43c10d4a849544d46f32e40d143b2f8/f46e7/github.png 340w,\n/static/d43c10d4a849544d46f32e40d143b2f8/ca1dc/github.png 680w,\n/static/d43c10d4a849544d46f32e40d143b2f8/e4da8/github.png 766w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>image-center</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>I've got plan to fill the 2021 in green!</p>\n<h2 id=\"2020\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2020\" aria-label=\"2020 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>2020</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The most important change - work!</li>\n<li>I learning <strong>Python</strong> from last few months - it's some repo which I store some exercises <a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/python\">python</a></li>\n<li>I learned a lot of AWS services - I done course of Sephane Maarek <a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/course/aws-certified-developer-associate-dva-c01/\">Ultimate AWS Certified Developer Associate 2021 - NEW!</a>, but it's to early to pass an exam without stress.</li>\n<li>I got some basic knowledge about DDD techniques. I read Domain-Driven Design in PHP and Domain-Driven Design Distilled (Vaughn Vernon)</li>\n<li>I have finished the one of the best book about programming (yep, today): 'Zrozumieć programowanie' (Gynvael Coldwind)</li>\n<li>I training a lot of programming. Besides of repo i practiced resolving some golf (from Coding Dojo Silesia) and other exercises\n<ul>\n<li>Coding Dojo Silesia events:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/gameoflife-kata\">Game of life - JS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/sql-engine-kata\">Sql engine - JS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/vending-machine-php\">Vending Machine - PHP - not finished</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>WarsawJS:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/warsawjs-workshop-43\">WarsawJS workshop 43 - intermediate javascript training</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/warsawjs-workshop-44-design-patterns\">WarsawJS Workshop #44 - Design Patterns</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/warsawjs-workshop-46-piotrek\">WarsawJS workshop #46 - Unit testing</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Docplanner Workshops:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/Docplanner_Tech_Workshops_1\">Bank - my implementation of Event Sourcing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/clean-code-architecture\">Clean Code workshop</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Others\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarcinGladkowski/bash-training\">Basics of Bash</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>I am sure, that was a lot of other things...</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>I participated in only one stationary conference (Boiling Frogs 2020) :/</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2021\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2021\" aria-label=\"2021 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>2021</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Keep going with Python and AWS services</li>\n<li>I want to create some IoT things (like magic mirror)</li>\n<li>Keep training programming languages a lot!</li>\n<li>And also practicing my speaking English.</li>\n<li>Do something for open source.</li>\n<li>Participate in some hackathon.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Marcin</em></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Summary 2020 - plans for 2021","date":"December 31, 2020","update":"December 31, 2020","tags":["personal"],"series":null},"fields":{"slug":"/summary-2020-plans-for-2021/","readingTime":{"minutes":1.695}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"57f2837d-042f-5460-8bb6-fd4495576bc2","fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hello world"}}},{"node":{"id":"15d38b46-7f4e-5d99-92b1-18b74982f8d2","fields":{"slug":"/warsawjs-desing-patterns/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"WarsawJs 44 Design patterns"}}},{"node":{"id":"e9bb0690-14f3-5e9f-9328-584c9f24e8c1","fields":{"slug":"/about/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"About"}}},{"node":{"id":"4ad66fcd-90b1-5304-a213-1c3fc30b256b","fields":{"slug":"/bash-training/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Bash training"}}},{"node":{"id":"48928a16-f1c5-5d1b-a33d-0f50d18db0ff","fields":{"slug":"/bash-training-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Bash training 2"}}},{"node":{"id":"3b607386-b659-5272-8fa3-ffa04fb840cb","fields":{"slug":"/summary-2020-plans-for-2021/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Summary 2020 - plans for 2021"}}},{"node":{"id":"6d347c29-ca14-5af3-9aec-3c7e8d0f7a69","fields":{"slug":"/clean-code-workshop